  # Build directories
  build-*/
  build/
  cmake-build-*/

  # Generated files
  *.o
  *.a
  *.so
  *.dylib
  *.dll
  *.exe
  *.app
  moc_*.cpp
  ui_*.h
  qrc_*.cpp
  *_autogen/

  # Package outputs
  *.deb
  *.rpm
  *.dmg
  *.tar.gz
  *.zip

  # IDE/Editor files
  .idea/
  .vscode/
  *.pro.user
  *.creator.user
  CMakeUserPresets.json

  # Dependencies/Submodules
  src/TetGen/

  # Translation binaries
  *.qm

  # OS files
  .DS_Store
  Thumbs.db

  # Logs and temp files
  *.log
  *.tmp
  *.swp
  *~

  # Documentation builds
  docs/_build/
  html/
  latex/

  # Test outputs
  Testing/
  CTestTestfile.cmake

  This ignores:
  - Build artifacts - compiled objects, libraries, executables
  - CMake generated files - autogen, moc, ui files
  - TetGen submodule - third-party mesh generator (large, external)
  - IDE configs - project-specific settings
  - Package outputs - installers you create
  - OS junk - .DS_Store, etc.

